  "mitigation_currently_implemented": "Deploy Snort IPS inline between UbuntuComputer and the network gateway to detect and block malicious exfiltration activity and archive file transfers over encrypted channels",
  "comments": "Added a Snort IPS device to the network and linked it upstream to the FortiGate firewall since UbuntuComputer had no available network slots for direct inline insertion. This allows Snort to monitor and block malicious traffic potentially related to the ongoing exfiltration from the compromised UbuntuComputer while the attacker remains present.",
  "device_identifier": "snort-ips-1",
